Nigerian Airports to Get Explosives Detectors, Punch Says

-- B y   V i n c e n t   N w a n m a
-- 
2011-07-11T10:17:36Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-11/nigerian-airports-to-get-explosives-detectors-punch-says.html
Airports in  Nigeria  will be equipped
with explosives detectors, Lagos-based  Punch  reported, citing
Stella Oduah-Ogiemwonyi, the newly appointed minister of
aviation.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Vincent Nwanma in Lagos at 
 vnwanma@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net . 